      "index": 1,
      "tag": "section",
      "className": "py-24 overflow-hidden",
      "text": "Builder The Easiest Content Builder Previously, building product tours required significant development effort. With Usertour, developers can quickly design, customize, and deploy product tours in minutes. Intuitive and Fully Visual Simply code, configure, and deploy—no unnecessary complexity involved. WYSIWYG editor Our rich content editor supports links, images, videos and user attributes. you can embed any content you want.",
