      "tag": "section",
      "className": "py-24 overflow-hidden",
      "text": "Theme Fully Customizable Themes With Usertour, you can tailor every detail to ensure your product tours integrate flawlessly with your application's look and feel. Personalized Colors and Fonts Adjust text, button colors, and more to match your branding. Select your preferred font family and size to maintain consistency. Support for Multiple Themes Design and manage multiple themes, applying them to different flows as needed for a cohesive user experience.",
