      "index": 4,
      "tag": "section",
      "className": "py-24 overflow-hidden",
      "text": "Personalize Personalize onboarding Leverage custom user attributes to tailor onboarding experiences to each user's unique needs and roles Multi-Language Compatibility Create a single flow and easily localize only the elements that differ across languages, streamlining global implementation. Automated Flow Triggers Set criteria to automatically initiate flows—such as when a user signs up, visits a specific page, or activates a feature—ensuring timely and relevant engagement.",
